      },
      "writtenOn": "2026-07-08T06:18:25Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "processPackage() previously caught sdbusplus exceptions around the whole operation. D-Bus object creation can now throw out of the inotify callback and leave partial state behind. Could we restore an outer exception handler that performs cleanup before returning an error?",
